Package: fetch
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Animated 3D fetch tool for your terminal
 A donut.c-inspired fetch tool that spins your distro logo in 3D with
 live-updating system info. Takes any ASCII/Unicode distro logo, turns
 each character into a point cloud based on its visual density, and
 renders it as a rotating 3D relief with Blinn-Phong shading. System
 info is gathered natively from /proc, /sys, and GTK config, with no
 external dependencies required.
